Package it.polimi.ingsw.Network

Class ServerConf

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.Network.ServerConf
public class ServerConf
extends java.lang.Object
Server configuration helper class. NB: the values here are the defaults. They can get overridden by the yaml conf, and the yaml conf can in turn be overridden by command line arguments.
